<tr><td>Infinite Lives</td><td>35370,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Lives = x</td><td>32817,x:35390,x (x= 1-255)</td></tr>
</table>
<BR><BR><B>Change x to whatever value you wish, using the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI</B>
