</td></tr>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Type-in hacks</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD>This can be found in <a href="ftp://ftp.void.jump.org/pub/sinclair/magazines/YourSinclair/Issue40/Tape/">this issue of Pokes</a> in the alphabetical section.
 <i>(Cover Tape in Your Sinclair issue 40)</i> 

<br><hr>
And how about some infinite lives then?
<pre>
 10 CLEAR 65535: LET T=0
 20 FOR F=3E4 TO 30016: READ A: POKE F,A
 30 NEXT F: READ A: IF T<>A THEN STOP
 40 RANDOMIZE USR 3E4
 50 DATA 205,86,5,221,33
 60 DATA 74,253,17,0,2
 70 DATA 62,255,55,205,86
 80 DATA 5,201,31811
 90 POKE 65289,0: POKE 65251,0
100 POKE 65175,0: POKE 65099,8
120 LET T=0: FOR F=65083 TO 65093
130 READ A: POKE F,A
140 LET T=T+(F- 65073)*A: NEXT F
150 READ A: IF T<>A THEN STOP
160 DATA 243,49,0,0,42
170 DATA 75,92,17,28,0
180 DATA 25,7447
190 LET T=0: FOR F=65313 TO 65319
200 READ A: POKE F,A
210 LET T=T+(F- 65303)*A: NEXT F
220 READ A: IF T<>A THEN STOP
230 RANDOMIZE USR 65083
240 DATA 175,50,42,138,195
250 DATA 148,91,11004
</pre>
 <i>(YS Smash Tips)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
